{"word":"G437 - ἀνθομολογέομαι - anthomologéomai - anth-om-ol-og-eh'-om-ahee - Give thanks","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνθομολογέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anthomologéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">anth-om-ol-og-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give thanks</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புகழ்"},{"paragraph":"to reply by professing, to agree mutually"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and the middle of <a href=\"#/G3670 - ὁμολογέω - homologéō - hom-ol-og-eh'-o/3670\">G3670</a>; to <i>confess in turn</i>, that is, <i>respond</i> in praise: - give thanks.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1843/1843\">G1843</a>, <a href=\"#/G3670/3670\">G3670</a>, <a href=\"#/G3671/3671\">G3671</a>, <a href=\"#/G3672/3672\">G3672</a>, <a href=\"#/G437/437\">G437</a>"}]}